      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for a daily driver. The engine and transmission are in solid working order, ensuring reliable performance for your commutes. However, please note that the exterior has several visible scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior upholstery shows noticeable wear from regular use. It has been maintained mechanically, though it lacks the cosmetic polish of a newer model. This car is ideal for someone prioritizing utility and mechanical dependability over aesthetics.",
