    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every trip. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of being well-loved, but it still looks great and runs even better! It's the perfect fit if you're looking for a dependable car that's ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
