      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring structural and timing reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power through the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings for precise turn-in. While displaying honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains robust with recent valve adjustments and consistent oil analysis results. A purist-spec build ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 32500.0,
