    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and drives great? This beauty has been so well-loved and is totally ready for its next big adventure. It's super clean, runs like a dream, and is honestly just a joy to be in. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car has got your back. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
