    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected from this analog icon. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car with a linear power band and exceptional throttle response.",
